{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3a4a14c9-ebd8-48e2-88d3-aa3a2b9da166","content":"This is a known MTP behavioral difference. **Exit code 8** means \"zero tests discovered,\" which MTP treats as an error by default — VSTest silently returned 0.\n\n**Fix:** Tell MTP to ignore exit code 8 by setting the `TESTINGPLATFORM_EXITCODE_IGNORE` environment variable, or by adding a property to your project file.\n\nThe simplest project-level fix:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01QnFyX2f7B83y6aRaczBKdV","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-e71e3f6ff58843edbaba65c63fc0a4c6/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n    <!-- Treat \"no tests discovered\" as success (matches VSTest behavior) -->\n    <TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-e71e3f6ff58843edbaba65c63fc0a4c6/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"a73860e3-f5d6-4543-b64f-d07e6e6fbb15","outputTokens":348,"requestId":"0BC8:15632C:4C646E:588361:69F005B4"},"id":"219428a5-4104-4ac7-bd86-97f63cee25f5","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:56:27.293Z","parentId":"615156d8-3596-4c53-ac38-db33d1302cd5"}
